{"tid":1514134,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英女王同意國會休會 約翰遜疑為硬脫歐鋪路","createTime":"2019-08-28T15:17:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T06:36:11.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"39388ac3bb82f8de9902a8a83f6ea47a472a0076","tid":1514134,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:17:05.000Z","msg":"英女王同意首相約翰遜要求，押後至10月14日才為國會新會期開幕大典致辭。英國國會休會期在9月結束，約翰遜的要求令國會休會至10月14日，屆時距離脫歐限期僅兩星期，有指這令議員沒有足夠時間商議防止在無協議下硬脫歐的方案。有親歐保守黨議員警告可對約翰遜提出不信任動議，有英媒指英國已陷提早大選邊緣。"},{"pid":"4e6346cb59138d45c2a4b6466bd2ae39341fd497","tid":1514134,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4aa828b63971f192193a2b0ddfc818917e2d54e","tid":1514134,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:17:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80798e021ea1f434de92f5e3e01c0c15c1a28344","tid":1514134,"uid":26491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:18:46.000Z","msg":"又不信任<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb039ec92898010697d31f479c64074f85a5b38","tid":1514134,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:19:18.000Z","msg":"又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"225e504eb467a92b269b71334c2afaa001f17b71","tid":1514134,"uid":78143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"repl